data.description: Embrace timeless nostalgia in this 1958 built residence spanning 1155 sq ft.  Offering 2/3 bedrooms and two full baths. The flexible layout includes a versatile room suitable for an additional bedroom, office, study, or flex room.  Enjoy the sunroom perfect for unwinding and the everyday convenience of the laundry room.   A spacious living room boasts wood floors and a large front window framing the charming front yard. The one car garage ensures practicality.  With the low maintenance yards and captivating Southwest curb appeal, this home seamlessly blends comfort and style for the discerning homeowner. Seller is offering a $2,000 credit that can be applied towards closing costs, improvements, or point buy down!  Check out the 3D tour today and schedule a tour!
